OL,5,G0200 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FThe prisoners hold a farwell party
OL,7,     Ffor Bea and Mum. Meg and Bill are
OL,8,     Fhaving problems with their teenage
OL,9,     Fson Marty. With Bea gone, Franky
OL,10,     Fannounces she is now in charge.
OL,11,G0300 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,12,     FWith Franky's hold growing in the
OL,13,     Fprison, temperatures reach boiling
OL,14,     Fpoint in an all-out riot in which
OL,15,     FBill gets stabbed.
OL,16,G0350 Entertainment News on 5
